    Welcome to SpaceX Launches ðŸš€! Here you can find all the information about
    SpaceX launches.
  </p>

  <nav
    class="flex flex-col items-center justify-between w-full text-center md:flex-row mt-5"
  >
    <HeaderButton class="text-white" href="/latest">
      <svg
        slot="before"
        class="bg-white rounded-full p-1"
        width="30"
        height="30"
        viewBox="0 0 24 24"
        stroke-width="1.5"
        stroke="#2c3e50"
        fill="none"
        stroke-linecap="round"
        stroke-linejoin="round"
      >
        <path stroke="none" d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="none"></path>
